  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: default gas price is different, when you go to \"Send transaction\" screen via /send command from chat with default fee OR when you go to \"Send transaction\" screen via \"Send\" from wallet, so seems that gas limit / gas price is calculated in different way.\r\n![gasprice](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34883373-24cfc7d2-f7c2-11e7-8ce0-b19a47d5ba22.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ndefault gas price is the same\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\ndefault gas price is different (20 GWEI / 21 GWEI)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\nPrerequisites: user has 0.1 ETH on balance and 1-1 chat\r\n\r\n1) \r\n- Open Status\r\n- Log in\r\n- Go to 1-1 chat\r\n- Tap on /send \r\n- Enter 0.003\r\n- Tap on blue button to send command\r\n- Tap on \"Advanced\". Check out Gas Price (can be 40 GWei, 20 Gwei)\r\n\r\n2) \r\n- Open Status\r\n- Log in\r\n- Go to Wallet\r\n- Tap on \"send\"\r\n- Choose any contact\r\n- Enter 0.003\r\n- Tap on \"Advanced\". Check out Gas Price (21 Gwei)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: \r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
